      "height": 220,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Bridge\n\nA bridge is an editor-facing capability object. Use the Properties panel for shallow operational control: target, kind, role, grants, and current exposure result. Use the editor drawer for deeper bridge design: target surface selection, exposure policy, key allowlists, scope, and explanatory notes.\n\nBridges should usually stay hidden in browser mode."
